<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1437,620,863]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
Note: Gnaspini (1996) suggested abandoning the use of subtribes because he found that 
<taxonomicName box="[1180,1362,693,719]" family="null" pageId="40" pageNumber="61" rank="subTribe" subTribe="Ptomaphaginina">Ptomaphaginina</taxonomicName>
is not monophyletic; however, 
<bibRefCitation author="Perreau, M." box="[513,745,729,755]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" pagination="1 - 460" refId="ref105064" refString="Perreau, M. (2000) Catalogue des Coleopteres Leiodidae Cholevinae et Platypsyllinae. Memoires de la Societe Entomologique de France, 4, 1 - 460." type="journal article" year="2000">Perreau (2000: 344)</bibRefCitation>
maintained its use and added a third, monotypic, subtribe, Baryodirina. The phylogenetic analysis of 
<bibRefCitation author="Antunes-Carvalho, C. &amp; Ribera, I. &amp; Beutel, R. G. &amp; Gnaspini, P." box="[721,1082,765,791]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" pagination="1 - 41" refId="ref98012" refString="Antunes-Carvalho, C., Ribera, I., Beutel, R. G. &amp; Gnaspini, P. (2019) Morphology-based phylogenetic reconstruction of Cholevinae (Coleoptera: Leiodidae): a new view on higher-level relationships. Cladistics, 35, 1 - 41. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / cla. 12230" type="journal article" year="2019">
Antunes-Carvalho 
<emphasis box="[937,997,765,791]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
recovered 
<taxonomicName authority="Perreau [2000]" authorityName="Perreau" authorityYear="2000" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Baryodirus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1214,1340,765,791]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Baryodirus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Perreau, M." pageId="40" pageNumber="41" pagination="1 - 460" refId="ref105064" refString="Perreau, M. (2000) Catalogue des Coleopteres Leiodidae Cholevinae et Platypsyllinae. Memoires de la Societe Entomologique de France, 4, 1 - 460." type="journal article" year="2000">Perreau [2000]</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
nested within “ 
<taxonomicName box="[475,666,801,827]" family="null" pageId="40" pageNumber="61" rank="subTribe" subTribe="Ptomaphaginina">Ptomaphaginina</taxonomicName>
”. We here maintain the use of subtribes.
</paragraph>
